China Lends Mozambique Funds for Low-Cost Housing, O Pais Says

-- B y   F r e d   K a t e r e r e
-- 
2011-09-20T05:47:32Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-20/china-lends-mozambique-funds-for-low-cost-housing-o-pais-says.html
China  will loan Mozambique 12
billion meticais ($439 million) to build 5,000 low-cost houses
near the capital, Maputo, O Pais reported, citing Mozambican
Prime Minister Aires Ali.  The project, which includes schools, health and commercial
centers, will be undertaken by Henan Gouji Industry and
Development of China, the newspaper said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Fred Katerere in Maputo at 
 fkaterere@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Paul Richardson at 
 pmrichardson@bloomberg.net  